/ Question Info ===============================================
/ Forming a Magic Square
/
/ Given a 3x3 matrix of integers:
/ - A magic square is a 3x3 grid where:
/   * All numbers are distinct and from 1 to 9
/   * Each row, column, and diagonal sums to the same value
/
/ Task:
/ - Convert the given matrix into a magic square
/ - Each change has a cost = absolute difference between values
/ - Return the minimum total cost
/ =============================================================